01:04:58.840 --> 01:04:59.840
[Amit Varma]: happen.

01:04:59.840 --> 01:05:00.840
[Amit Varma]: So that's amazing.

01:05:00.840 --> 01:05:05.720
[Amit Varma]: Let me sort of I've taken a lot of your time, let me end with a dual question that is almost

01:05:05.720 --> 01:05:10.120
[Amit Varma]: a cliche now, but I ask all guests of my show on whatever subject they're talking about,

01:05:10.120 --> 01:05:12.280
[Amit Varma]: is that what makes you despair?

01:05:12.280 --> 01:05:16.680
[Amit Varma]: And what makes you hopeful about the future of gay rights in India?

01:05:16.680 --> 01:05:21.280
[Guest]: So the ignorance that we still have in the country with regards to gay rights, when I

01:05:21.280 --> 01:05:25.720
[Guest]: talk to people about Section 377, they don't have any idea what that law is.

01:05:25.720 --> 01:05:29.560
[Guest]: Some people don't know a gay friend also, they don't have any kind of common sense.

01:05:29.560 --> 01:05:31.560
[Amit Varma]: Or if they do, they don't know that they know a gay friend.

01:05:31.560 --> 01:05:32.560
[Amit Varma]: Exactly.

01:05:32.560 --> 01:05:33.560
[Amit Varma]: And that's doubly tragic.

01:05:33.560 --> 01:05:34.560
[Guest]: Yeah.

01:05:34.560 --> 01:05:38.880
[Guest]: So that is a lot of despair there, because I hope that everybody gets to feel the way

01:05:38.880 --> 01:05:42.800
[Guest]: I get to feel, you know, and I'm entitled and I'm happy that way.

01:05:42.800 --> 01:05:47.960
[Guest]: But not many people can afford to like come out so easily, which is making me sadder.

01:05:47.960 --> 01:05:52.520
[Guest]: And what makes me hopeful is that there's a very strong ally movement in this country,

01:05:52.520 --> 01:05:57.840
[Guest]: people, women, especially, who have felt the same kind of, you know, the society's rebuked

01:05:57.840 --> 01:05:59.600
[Guest]: them on a certain level.

01:05:59.600 --> 01:06:00.600
[Guest]: So they understand.

01:06:00.600 --> 01:06:05.440
[Guest]: So I've made such great friendship with women who are so admirable in their own way, and

01:06:05.440 --> 01:06:09.480
[Guest]: they go out of their way to help me out, deal with my own mental anxiety.

01:06:09.480 --> 01:06:12.240
[Amit Varma]: And because they're also victims, and they're fighting society in their own way.

01:06:12.240 --> 01:06:16.120
[Guest]: So I found the strongest women in this country have been my strongest allies in some way

01:06:16.120 --> 01:06:17.160
[Guest]: or the other.

01:06:17.160 --> 01:06:22.000
[Guest]: And even men who go on the femme side, I find them so adorable in their own way, you know,

01:06:22.000 --> 01:06:25.960
[Guest]: like people, whenever they tell you like, that whole Biola tag is gone from my head

01:06:25.960 --> 01:06:26.960
[Guest]: entirely now.

